/ Header
%header.rounded-5.bg-secondary.py-7.header-image.mb-5
  .container.px-4.px-lg-5.my-5
  .text-left.text-white.m-5
    .row
      .col-md-8.border-end.shadow
        %div
          %h1.display-4.fw-bolder RAFIQ GENERAL TRADING
          %p.lead.fw-normal.text-white-50.mb-2 U.K LTD (RGT UK LTD)
          %h1.display-4 House Hold Products
          %h1.display-4.mb-2 To Your Doorsteps
          %p
            We believe in providing you with products that will help you in everyday life for the rest of your life.
            Browse our website and see what we have to offer. Like something? We deliver! Simply add it to your cart and post a request.
            Our designated team will be in contact with you within 24-hours.
          .btn.btn-dark.rounded-5 Show Products

      .col-md-4
        .container
          .card.m-4{style: "border-radius: 15px; background-color: #053768; color: white; width:100%"}
            .card-body
              %h3.card-title Since 1995
              %p.lead.fw-normal.text-white-50.mb-2 All rights reserved.
              %p We are recognised by the UK government as official providers for household products.Our credentials are proof of our authenticity, genuineness and commitment to our clients
              %p We at Rafiq General Trading L.L.C are committed to provide you with the best products to make your life easy. Browse our products for more information on what we provide.
  

